The question was asked: Why another remake? There are no good answers. I've enjoyed surfing for a long time with one of my interests being surfing for tricks in skyworld. I decided to open a server in October and wanted something that would draw players from that group and as with the countless remakes there are countless skyworld servers. At the same time I wondered what exactly a skyworld with smooth ramps would play like and quite reasonably was getting tired of the skybox having played it for two years. Two birds with one stone, problem solved. Necessary? No, but the map has served its purpose well enough and so I am content with it. It's no work of art, no long hours of creative input, and based on merit of the map's qualities alone, not worthy of a great rating. I didn't try to make this anything more than it is, no useless ramps/platforms/etc. Just a simple edit for a simple purpose. 

-The main/awp ramps are now smooth and completely two-way surfable.
-M3 under each water platform.
-M249 under spawn.
-AK/M4 at bottom pool.
-Ammo in all weapons.

I know a lot of people will probably feel like drilling me into the ground for remaking this map, but I've seen it on a decent number of servers, so I figured for look/fun's sake, I'd rebuild it from scratch.

Everything in this remake is built from scratch using a ripped .bsp as a "skeleton" for lack of a better word.

This maps plays exactly the same as the original, so there should be no problems with changes in surf or gameplay.  One thing I did add was a bombsite on top of the house that holds all the weapons of the map, to ensure that rounds end in a timely manner.

Other then that, this is just a nice clean, new feel to skyscraper, and I hope you all enjoy it!

I made this map in one day

Brief Summery 
Freestyle kill map with 2 bombsites. There is many different ways to the bottom. Which is where the jail is, and above the jail are many different landings. The 2 main landings offer unlimited shotguuns and scouts. From those two landings you can TP to the 4 corners of the upper castle. From those 4 corners you may not find them right away, but there are "multiple" Lines that will give you enough speed to make it to the bombsites. Which are above shotgun and scoutlandings. here is a pic of where the bombsites are: 
http://surfsource.clanservers.com/screenpics/surf_skycastle0001.jpg 
Where the ak's and colt's are is the bombsites. 
There is also a few jailbreaks. I will inform you of 2. 
1. Is an automatic jailbreak. every 45 seconds the back gate will open up. Step into the fire to TP to the next level. You will hear a siron right before the gate opens. 
2. If there are 2 players in jail. You can boost to the bottom of this env_beam in middle of jail. Which will TP infront of a button where you can open the front gate in jail. 
Here is a Pic of where to boost, and gate thats on a timer: 
http://surfsource.clanservers.com/screenpics/surf_skycastle0000.jpg 

There are a few other secrets. Unfortunately nothing as cool as the LSS in RR. 

Here is a list of all the guns in the map. 
Unlimited Pump shotties 
Unlimited Scouts 
3 colts 
3 AKs 
2 Mac10s 
2 sets of dulies 
2 5/7s (maybe they are p220 I don't remember) 
4 Nades 
2 Flashes 
2 Smoke nades 
4 Autosnipes 
2 Para 
4 Defusal Kits 
1 AWP (the only way to get awp and PARA is to make it to the top landing on the 3rd level of ramps.)

surf_skybears_lighted

Link to the normal version of surf_skybears. Be carefull !! This map is made for normal surf servers + RPG. Certainly NOT for DM. This is without HDR but lighted, the hdr version was around 40MB Noblock required ! Fixed or changed things
  • Added light, but not hdr <.<
  • I made the rounds 1 min shorter
  • The knife round won't fail with a rpg mod now
Gameplay: Ct's and t's spawn at each side of spawn without any weapons: There are 3 ways to surf: At the noob way, there's a cannon: You just need to walk in the loop and it fires you! Can't be easier^^ When you are shot, you get a knife. Now we have the Pro way, it's hard to surf but fast. The extreme way are 3 stages + bonus This version is much darker in the extreme way! After 5 minutes, everyone in here will be teleported to jail and the jail teleport will be disabled. And when you teleport, you get one of these weapons: stage 1 - Knife stage 2 - deagle stage 3 - shotgun stage 4 - m4a1 Stage 1 Stage 2 Stage 3 (The bonus is rather fun to surf) There's also a small secret at the end of the bonus. And in that secret you can set the next round to 'knives only'! I made a tutorial about this: TUTORIAL WARNING:It will fail if there's a DM mod installed on the server Please enjoy!
